The following people have contributed to LLVM-Z80:

Chanung Park (Kiroo, @zlfn) (ung@zlfn.space) — Z80/SM83 backend, runtime libraries
Alex Jokela (alex@camulus.com) — Initial Z80 backend port

The LLVM-Z80 project incorporates code from the LLVM-MOS project
(https://github.com/llvm-mos/llvm-mos), whose contributors include:

Daniel Thornburgh (mysterymath@gmail.com)
Jack Andersen (jackoalan@gmail.com)
John Byrd (jbyrd@giganticsoftware.com)
Adrian Siekierka (kontakt@asie.pl)
Nolan Check (beholdnec@gmail.com)
Piotr Fusik (piotr@fusion-lang.org)
Mikael Lund (Mlund@mac.com)
Mariusz Kryński (mrk@sed.pl)

Built, of course, upon the amazing work of the LLVM Project Authors!
